text: Onolbaataryn Khulan is a basketball player from Mongolia. Khulan competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Khulan ONOLBAATAR She was born on 27 July 1999.Onolbaatar Khulan == References == Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian basketball players Category:Olympians for Mongolia
